{"text": "Technology ke saath mera pehla experience bachpan mein tha jab maine pehli baar computer dekha tha. Main bahut excited tha aur mouse ko touch karne se darta tha kyunki mujhe lagta tha kuch kharab ho jayega. Jab maine pehli baar internet use kiya, main ghanton website browse karta raha aur time ka pata hi nahi chala. Aaj smartphone itna common ho gaya hai ke main soch bhi nahi sakta ke iske bagair kaise zindagi guzarti thi. Technology ne hamari zindagi ko itna asaan bana diya hai ke ab hum har cheez ke liye digital solutions dhundte hain."}

{"text": "Saal 2040 mein, Maya apne smart glasses pehen kar virtual office mein login hui jahan uske colleagues duniya bhar se holographic form mein mojud thay. Uski AI assistant ne use yaad dilaya ke aaj uska appointment hai climate restoration center mein jahan wo apne carbon credits check karega. Shaam ko wo apne electric flying car mein betha aur Mars colony ke saath video call kiya jahan uska bhai engineer ka kaam kar raha tha. Raat ke waqt, wo apne rooftop garden mein gaya jahan genetically modified plants oxygen produce kar rahe thay aur pollution filter kar rahe thay. Sone se pehle usne apne brain-computer interface se kal ke liye dreams program kiye taake wo space exploration ke bare mein sapne dekh sake."}

{"text": "AI creative response tasks mein humans ko replace kar sakta hai kyunki yeh vast data se patterns identify kar sakta hai aur unique combinations generate kar sakta hai. AI speed aur consistency mein humans se behtar hai, 24/7 kaam kar sakta hai, aur bias se free ho sakta hai. Machine learning algorithms creative writing, art, aur music mein impressive results dikha rahe hain. AI human limitations jaise fatigue aur emotional blocks se mukt hai, aur infinite variations produce kar sakta hai jo humans ke liye mushkil hai."}

{"text": "Numbers ke set ka median calculate karne ka tareeqa: Pehle saare numbers ko ascending order mein arrange kariye. Agar numbers ki total count odd hai, to middle wala number median hai. Agar count even hai, to middle ke do numbers ka average nikaal kar median milega. Misal ke tor par: 3,5,7,9,11 mein median 7 hai. Aur 2,4,6,8 mein median (4+6)/2 = 5 hai."}
